Question: Dongguan Dongsong Electronic Co., Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Dongguan Dongsong Electronic Co., Ltd.

Product: Power Supplies

- Power range from 3W to 480W
- Level VI energy efficiency compliance
- Widely used in Computer Peripherals & Communication Devices, Audio & Video Apparatus, Small home appliances, Medical equipment, LED drivers, and Chargers
- Full certifications for safety and environmental protection
- High efficiency and low standby power consumption
- Skilled and experienced R&D team
- ISO9001 and ISO14001 certified factory
- Professional safety and quality testing laboratory
- Compliance with international safety and quality standards such as UL, FCC, CE, RoHS, REACH, and PAHs
- Customized power solutions available
- Recognized as a National High-tech Enterprise
- Wide range of products including audio power supplies, IT power supplies, open-frame power supplies, multi-port USB chargers, and LED drivers
- Prominent sales growth in American, European, and Australian markets
- Widely used in various electronic devices and equipment
